messages.content: What is the purpose of the comfyui-faster-loading extension?
The comfyui-faster-loading extension aims to accelerate the loading of checkpoints with ComfyUI.
How can checkpoints be accelerated with ComfyUI?
The comfyui-faster-loading extension facilitates faster loading of checkpoints in ComfyUI.
What is the GitHub repository where the comfyui-faster-loading extension can be found?
The comfyui-faster-loading extension can be found on GitHub at https://github.com/nonnonstop/comfyui-faster-loading.git.
What is the installation command for the comfyui-faster-loading extension?
The installation command for the comfyui-faster-loading extension is `cd ComfyUI/custom_nodes && git clone https://github.com/nonnonstop/comfyui-faster-loading.git`.
Where should the installation of the comfyui-faster-loading extension be made within ComfyUI?
The installation of the comfyui-faster-loading extension should be made within the `custom_nodes` directory of ComfyUI.
What issue are they addressing with the comfyui-faster-loading extension?
The comfyui-faster-loading extension addresses the issue mentioned in the GitHub repository at https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/issues/1992.
